---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Count Easy - Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Count Easy - Countdown & Days Tracker iOS app."
  ogUrl="https://idlefusion.com/count-easy/privacy"
>
  <main>
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-12">Count Easy - Countdown & Days Tracker &middot; Effective February 15, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
            <p>Count Easy does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. Everything stays on your device.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
            <p>All your countdowns, categories, settings, and preferences are stored locally on your device using SwiftData. No data is sent to any server, cloud service, or third party. There are no user accounts and no sign-up required.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">No HealthKit</h2>
            <p>Count Easy does not integrate with Apple HealthKit. The app does not read or write any health-related data.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">No Cloud Sync</h2>
            <p>Count Easy does not use iCloud sync, CloudKit, or any other cloud service to sync your data between devices. Your countdowns exist only on the device where you created them. Standard iOS device backups may include app data if you have backups enabled.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Analytics & Tracking</h2>
            <p>Count Easy contains no analytics frameworks, no ad SDKs, no tracking pixels, and no telemetry of any kind. We do not use any third-party services that collect data.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Network Usage</h2>
            <p>Count Easy makes no network requests. The app works entirely offline. The only network activity associated with the app is through the App Store for updates.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Widgets</h2>
            <p>Count Easy's widgets display your countdown data on your home screen and lock screen. This data is read from local storage and is never transmitted over the network.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>Count Easy does not knowingly collect any information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>If this policy changes, we will update this page with the new effective date. Since Count Easy collects no data, meaningful changes are unlikely.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@idlefusion.com" class="text-[var(--accent-primary)] hover:underline">support@idlefusion.com</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
